IronWifi,provides,network,authentication,service,via,hosted,RADIUS,servers,that,can,be,deployed,within,minutes,The,API,provides,authentication,for,users,visitors,or,mobile,devices,before,allowing,access,to,network,resources,It,also,allows,for,requirements,to,have,access,to,resources,such,as,maximum,allowed,data,to,download,or,bandwidth,that,the,client,may,consume